  'Far Niente Chardonnay|Burrata': 'Far Niente — Oakville Chardonnay with buttered citrus, toasted hazelnut, crème brûlée, lush texture. The opulent oak is heavier than burrata needs — the lush weight threatens to crush the delicate cheese, though the hazelnut does play against pistachio. Strong with restraint — lighter Chards peak higher.',
