  'Keenan Mernet|Roast Half Chicken': 'Spring Mountain Napa Mernet — Merlot-Cab, mountain structure, plush dark cherry, plum, medium tannin. The plush body plays against roasted chicken\'s skin-and-jus build; preparation changes seasonally — check with kitchen for today\'s build. Works as mountain Merlot-Cab for chicken — Keenan story on the bird course.',
