  'Keenan Mernet|Shrimp Cocktail': 'Spring Mountain Napa Mernet against cold raw shrimp with horseradish — mountain-grown Merlot-Cab and chilled shellfish with cocktail sauce is textbook clash. Never pair. Route shrimp cocktail to Chardonnay, Sauvignon Blanc, Rosé, or Champagne; keep Keenan Mernet for the steak course.',
