  'Lail Vineyards Daniel Cuvée|The Tomahawk': 'Lail flagship multi-appellation Napa Cab — Howell/Calistoga/Oakville/Stags Leap, dark fruit, cassis, graphite, dried violet, firm tannin, full body. The firm tannin handles Tomahawk\'s massive bone-in ribeye and the graphite plays against smoky char. Peak historically-significant Napa Cab for Tomahawk — Daniel Cuvée pedigree on the grand cut.',
