  'Le Ragnaie Brunello|Cowboy Ribeye': 'Tuscany Brunello di Montalcino DOCG Sangiovese Grosso — Le Ragnaie, five years minimum aging, dried cherry, tobacco, leather, rose petal, full body, firm tannin. The full body handles ribeye\'s big marbled build and the leather plays against beefy char. Strong Italy\'s-most-prestigious for ribeye — Brunello on the bold cut.',
