  'Poderi Aldo Conterno Nebbiolo|Filet Mignon': 'Piedmont Barolo DOCG Nebbiolo — Aldo Conterno Bussia Monforte d\'Alba, rose petal, tar, dried cherry, orange peel, iron minerality, full body, firm tannin, high acid, age-worthy. The firm tannin meets butter-tender filet\'s delicate sweetness and the orange peel plays against escargot-butter. Peak serious-Barolo for filet — one of Barolo\'s greatest names on the delicate cut.',
